column5: GOT OUT FOR A FEW HRS THIS MORN!!! MORN WAS PRETTY SLOW TILL THE SUN GOT UP AND STARTED TO WARM THINGS UP ABIT!!! NO MONSTERS BUT SOME REAL DECENT BASS WERE BOARDED!!           BUDDY SNUCK A PIC OF ME IN FLIPPIN THE LILIES!!! (GETTIN OLD NEED THE GLASSES  LOL)
looks like a good day of fishing,congrats
Nice.  and nice area too.  I just don't care to fish in those lilies...forever getting snagged.
I can relate to that CC.  Nice catching there. Got to love those pad bites.
Great report! Most people find Scugog a tough place to fish, so you did pretty good.  cheers,  ehg
